We're out to changethe way the world gets power











Making clean,Solar energy accessible for all

Founded in 2006, SolarCity has revolutionized the way energy is delivered--providing homeowners, businesses, schools and governments a more affordable and sustainable alternative to electricity from utilities.
As America's largest solar provider, we continue to help people take control of their energy costs and decrease their carbon footprint.






Simplifying Solar

When we set out to transform the way people get power, we knew we had to make the process as simple as possible. That's why we handle every aspect of a project from start to finish. And we back it all up with the best warranty in the industry and a performance guarantee for the life of the contract.
Learn More














Solar ona national scale

SolarCity currently offers service in many states throughout the country. And we don't just generate clean energy in those states--we generate local jobs that strengthen communities. Our customers include over 300,000 homeowners, more than 400 schools and universities, thousands of businesses, as well as government entities of all sizes.
See if we're in your area.














Giving power to thosewho need it most

In 2014, SolarCity founded the GivePower Foundation, a nonprofit organization dedicated to bringing clean, reliable energy to the developing world. GivePower helps create better lives for people in impoverished communities through the power of solar--from improving access to food and water to better equipping health centers to increasing opportunities for students and entrepreneurs.












  

