Payment options









Ways To Pay






Option 1: Loan
Invest in the cost of the system and save over time. With a $0-down payment, simply pay for your system every month at a low, fixed cost. We cover installation, roof warranty and energy monitoring. Any benefits from available tax credits go straight to you.


Option 2: Cash
Buy the system outright and own the energy from day one. We cover installation, roof warranty and energy monitoring. Any benefits from available tax credits go straight to you.


Option 3: Lease
Get a low, fixed monthly payment with predictable costs and consistent savings. Choose to prepay your lease partially, or in full for added savings. We cover installation, roof warranty and energy monitoring.


Option 4: PPA
Pay for the energy produced each month at an industry-low rate. We cover installation, roof warranty and energy monitoring.











