Why Go Solar?

Control Energy Costs
With solar you can secure predictable electricity costs for years to come.
Save Money
In most states, solar costs less than energy from the utility, so you can save on your bill.
Help the Environment
Solar creates 91% less CO2 pollution than natural gas and 96% less CO2 than coal.
Energy Independence
Clean solar energy provides us with an unlimited, reliable source of energy.




Why SolarCity?

We've powered over 300,000 homes
Trusted by more homeowners in the U.S. than any other solar company.
Best Warranty Ever
The longest warranty coverage in the industry also guarantees the performance of your system.
We Make it Affordable
Our industry-leading financing options make it easy to switch to solar.
We've Got Your Back Up
The Powerwall gives your family peace of mind that’s affordable and reliable.









5 Simple Steps to go Solar

We make it easy to switch to solar. Our dedicated team will handle everything from start to finish. We’ll even assign a solar concierge to your project who will guide you through the process and keep you informed about what’s happening every step of the way. It all begins with a quick consultation.









1
Solar Consultation
We’ll talk to see if solar is right for you and create a free quote based on your energy usage and satellite images of your roof.




2
Agreement
You’ll secure predictable solar costs for years to come depending on your payment  option. No hidden fees or worries thanks to our incredible warranty.




3
System Design
We’ll visit your home to examine your roof and take measurements. Then, our engineers will design a custom system to meet your energy needs.




4
Installation
Most solar installations take one day. Our solar concierge handles everything from permits to inspections.




5
Activation
Once the utility gives approval, you can start generating your own clean, renewable energy.










Power your world, your way

Get control over energy costs and save on your monthly bill while making your planet a better place with clean, renewable energy.


