^ a b Ivory, Danielle; Cardwell, Diane (2017-02-22). "SolarCity’s Ties to Foreclosure Cases Raise Questions on Vetting Policies". The New York Times. ISSN 0362-4331. Retrieved 2017-03-17. 
^ a b c d Grind, Kirsten (2017-05-03). "SEC Probes Solar Companies Over Disclosure of Customer Cancellations". Wall Street Journal. ISSN 0099-9660. Retrieved 2017-05-05. 
^ "Advocacy group briefs FBI in Arizona Corporation Commission inquiry". Arizona Republic. 2016-07-06. Retrieved 2016-07-22. 
^ SolarCity Announces Proposed Securitization Company press release, 4 November 2013
