SolarCity

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia


					Jump to:					navigation, 					search

Not to be confused with Solar Cities in Australia or City Solar.

SolarCity





Type

Subsidiary


Industry
Energy storage


Founded
July 4, 2006; 11 years ago (2006-07-04)


