^ Robinson, David (December 5, 2016). "SolarCity begins its hunt for factory workers". The Buffalo News. Retrieved 2016-12-09. 
^ "The Alliance for Solar Choice - About Us". TASC. Archived from the original on 2013-11-03. Retrieved 2015-03-10. 


